chain_source

Class Best_Match_Results

  • java.lang.Object
    • chain_source.Best_Match_Results

  • public class Best_Match_Results
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for taking results after calling SPSM and then filtering to ensure each result is over the determined threshold, cut the number of results to the desired n and sort so that the match with the highest similarity is at the top of the list This class is tested in Match_Results_Test_Cases.java and SPSM_Filter_Results_Test_Cases.java
    Author:
    Tanya Howden, Diana Bental (Modified November 2017)
